ZH: 水稻是一种主要的粮食作物。
EN: Rice is a major staple crop.

ZH: 我家种了一大片水稻田。
EN: My family grows a large area of rice paddies.

ZH: 今年的水稻收成不错。
EN: This year's rice harvest is good.

ZH: 水稻需要充足的水源和阳光。
EN: Rice needs an adequate water supply and sunlight.

ZH: 虽然气候不够暖和，但是这个地区的水稻种植面积仍然很大。
EN: Although the climate is not warm enough, the area still has a large area for rice cultivation.

ZH: 水稻需要定期浇水。
EN: Rice needs regular watering.

ZH: 我喜欢在水稻田里散步。
EN: I enjoy taking a walk in the rice paddies.

ZH: 这里的水稻长势非常好。
EN: The rice here is growing very well.

ZH: 每年春季，我们都要播种水稻。
EN: We plant rice every spring.

ZH: 在中国，水稻是主食之一。
EN: In China, rice is one of the staple foods.

ZH: 每当收割水稻的时候，农民们都很忙碌。
EN: Farmers are busy when it's time to harvest rice.

ZH: 水稻的生长需要耐心和细心照料。
EN: The growth of rice requires patience and careful attention.

ZH: 水稻在适宜的环境下能茁壮成长。
EN: Rice can thrive in suitable environments.

ZH: 这个地区的气候适合水稻的生长。
EN: The climate in this area is suitable for rice cultivation.

ZH: 我们家的水稻田里有很多螃蟹。
EN: There are many crabs in our rice paddy fields.

ZH: 水稻是与亚热带和热带地区相关的主要农作物。
EN: Rice is a major crop associated with subtropical and tropical regions.

ZH: 在泥土里插种水稻种子需要一定技巧。
EN: Planting rice seeds in the soil requires some skill.

ZH: 本地区的水稻产量每年都在增加。
EN: The rice production in this region is increasing every year.

ZH: 时间到了，该收割水稻了。
EN: It's time to harvest the rice.

ZH: 我们需要给水稻施肥。
EN: We need to fertilize the rice.
